snippet: Two young boys playing on a Sydney beach on Sunday found an infant's body buried in the sand, police said, one week after a newborn baby was discovered alive at the bottom of a drain in the city's suburbs....

headline.print_headline: Boys Discover Baby's Body Buried at Sydney Beach
headline.main: Boys Discover Baby's Body Buried at Sydney Beach

lead_paragraph: Two young boys playing on a Sydney beach on Sunday found an infant's body buried in the sand, police said, one week after a newborn baby was discovered alive at the bottom of a drain in the city's suburbs.
